      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "This is repeated 3 times: for `noban`, `noban,download` and `download,noban`. Could avoid the repetitions with something like:\r\n\r\n```cpp\r\nNetWhitebindPermissions noban;\r\nNetWhitebindPermissions noban_download;\r\nNetWhitebindPermissions download_noban;\r\n\r\nTryParse(\"noban@...\", noban);\r\n...all 6 checks...\r\n\r\nTryParse(\"noban,download@...\", noban_download);\r\nBOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(noban_download, noban); // just this instead of the 6 repeated checks\r\n\r\nTryParse(\"download,noban@...\", download_noban);\r\nBOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(download_noban, noban); // just this instead of the 6 repeated checks\r\n```",
      "commit_id" : "693af714ea264cd5edeadecaa0e7762cfe377e5a",
      "created_at" : "2021-04-14T07:25:20Z",
      "diff_hunk" : "@@ -395,6 +395,51 @@ BOOST_AUTO_TEST_CASE(netpermissions_test)\n     BOOST_CHECK(NetWhitebindPermissions::TryParse(\"@1.2.3.4:32\", whitebindPermissions, error));\n     BOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_NONE);\n \n+    // \"noban\" implies \"download\"\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetWhitebindPermissions::TryParse(\"noban@1.2.3.4:32\", whitebindPermissions, error));\n+    BOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_NOBAN);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(whitebindPermissions.m_flags & PF_DOWNLOAD);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(whitebindPermissions.m_flags & PF_NOBAN);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetPermissions::HasFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_DOWNLOAD));\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetPermissions::HasFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_NOBAN));\n+\n+    NetPermissions::ClearFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_DOWNLOAD);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(!(whitebindPermissions.m_flags & PF_DOWNLOAD));\n+    BOOST_CHECK(whitebindPermissions.m_flags & PF_NOBAN);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(!NetPermissions::HasFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_DOWNLOAD));\n+    BOOST_CHECK(!NetPermissions::HasFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_NOBAN));\n+\n+    // \"noban,download\" is equivalent to \"noban\"\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetWhitebindPermissions::TryParse(\"noban,download@1.2.3.4:32\", whitebindPermissions, error));\n+    BOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_NOBAN);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(whitebindPermissions.m_flags & PF_DOWNLOAD);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(whitebindPermissions.m_flags & PF_NOBAN);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetPermissions::HasFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_DOWNLOAD));\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetPermissions::HasFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_NOBAN));\n+\n+    // \"download,noban\" is equivalent to \"noban\"\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetWhitebindPermissions::TryParse(\"download,noban@1.2.3.4:32\", whitebindPermissions, error));\n+    BOOST_CHECK_EQUAL(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_NOBAN);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(whitebindPermissions.m_flags & PF_DOWNLOAD);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(whitebindPermissions.m_flags & PF_NOBAN);\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetPermissions::HasFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_DOWNLOAD));\n+    BOOST_CHECK(NetPermissions::HasFlag(whitebindPermissions.m_flags, PF_NOBAN));",
